    {
      "id": "6WUFM32c98M-18vKwBmuM",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 923.8153670299572,
      "y": 2471.1482154571477,
      "width": 556.4159545898438,
      "height": 120,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 80,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b73",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 481438286,
      "version": 13192,
      "versionNonce": 998163410,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774360997900,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "** The different types of roles: \n\n- thesis: The central thesis of the author that needs to be analyzed. \n- argument: Supports the thesis. Can also be a sub-argument. \n- counterargument: Opposes the thesis or an argument. \n",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "** The different types of roles: \n\n- thesis: The central thesis of the author that needs to be analyzed. \n- argument: Supports the thesis. Can also be a sub-argument. \n- counterargument: Opposes the thesis or an argument. \n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "uDlGmc8Klm_QS7TNYbIhV",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 930.2777976087708,
      "y": 599.5676295045575,
      "width": 409.6959228515625,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 40,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b74",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1990988178,
      "version": 1509,
      "versionNonce": 612311634,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774177099409,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Before continuing, we must check that there IS a \nthesis, that claims support other claims that exist, \nthat there is no closed loop. \n\nIt outputs a DAG: Directed Acyclic Graph. ",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Before continuing, we must check that there IS a \nthesis, that claims support other claims that exist, \nthat there is no closed loop. \n\nIt outputs a DAG: Directed Acyclic Graph. ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "SiDvAmiFXrjeocLEpzED0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 931.3085289335589,
      "y": 504.8218493396664,
      "width": 418.2879943847656,
      "height": 80,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 40,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b75",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1126129682,
      "version": 1760,
      "versionNonce": 2057488270,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774177086103,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Instructions: Go from top to bottom. First identify \nthe thesis (there should not be a lot of them), then \nidentify its supporting claims etc., forming a tree-like\ngraph. Depth shouldn't exceed 3. ",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Instructions: Go from top to bottom. First identify \nthe thesis (there should not be a lot of them), then \nidentify its supporting claims etc., forming a tree-like\ngraph. Depth shouldn't exceed 3. ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
